    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093380/extras/16f92c2d5d3098210cb79cf04efc8fe3.avif?t=1771250954\" width=600 height=112 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093380/extras/2d06d28e8cc6798f9da739c158ef92b8.poster.avif?t=1771250954\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093380/extras/2d06d28e8cc6798f9da739c158ef92b8.webm?t=1771250954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093380/extras/2d06d28e8cc6798f9da739c158ef92b8.mp4?t=1771250954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >参加自动战斗</h2>位置非常关键：战斗结果取决于你的战前设置、角色能力和你的命令。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093380/extras/384bf2fbf6d9e32c517be39a0d8c3155.poster.avif?t=1771250954\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093380/extras/384bf2fbf6d9e32c517be39a0d8c3155.webm?t=1771250954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093380/extras/384bf2fbf6d9e32c517be39a0d8c3155.mp4?t=1771250954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >利用环境</h2>让战场变成你的优势：建造尖刺墙，在城市废墟中建立阻塞点，将敌人诱入陷阱，将他们推向危险地带或地雷。谁说这种手段不公平？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093380/extras/18f2e4bf5985d39692194dfed3e2d831.poster.avif?t=1771250954\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093380/extras/18f2e4bf5985d39692194dfed3e2d831.webm?t=1771250954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093380/extras/18f2e4bf5985d39692194dfed3e2d831.mp4?t=1771250954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >组建你的小队</h2>指挥一支由各种各样的角色组成的队伍，学习如何使用他们的能力和战斗形态，并利用强大的植入体和装备（如能量护盾和时间武器）来增强他们的实力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093380/extras/a58b0893dab0076b916e5212d509a30c.poster.avif?t=1771250954\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093380/extras/a58b0893dab0076b916e5212d509a30c.webm?t=1771250954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093380/extras/a58b0893dab0076b916e5212d509a30c.mp4?t=1771250954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >了解你的敌人</h2>抵御致命的劫掠者，智取叛变者，猎杀危险的外星人，获取战利品和荣誉。各种敌人、地形和战斗目标都要求你随机应变。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093380/extras/d2574a716fe4f314ffcc8ff67d4f9544.poster.avif?t=1771250954\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093380/extras/d2574a716fe4f314ffcc8ff67d4f9544.webm?t=1771250954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093380/extras/d2574a716fe4f314ffcc8ff67d4f9544.mp4?t=1771250954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发展你的基地</h2>解锁新的物品、角色和派系，与之互动——从冷酷无情的骑士团到无所不知的 PFS。实验与制造协同效应带来的可能性是无限的：两次远征绝不会给你相同的感觉。",
